           SHORT="a simple and fast image viewer widget for GTK+"
cat << EOF
GtkImageView is a simple and fast image viewer widget for GTK+. Similar to
the image viewer panes in gThumb or Eye of Gnome. It makes writing image
viewing and editing applications easy. Among its features are:

* Mouse and keyboard zooming.  * Scrolling and dragging.  * Adjustable
interpolation.  * Fullscreen mode.  * GIF animation support.  * Ability to
make selections.  * Extensible using a tool system.

Bindings exists for Perl and Python and incomplete ones for C++.
EOF
